item.title: Projects
item.description: Projects Squeeze-and-excitation Networks: TensorFlow implementation of Squeeze-and-excitation blocks on different convolutional neural networks such as ResNet-18, ResNeXt-29 and InceptionV3 using CIFAR-10, CIFAR-100 and Tiny ImageNet. [Report]. Image classification using merged CNNs - Kaggle challenge: a use of two merged pre-trained convolutional neural networks (ResNet-50V2 and InceptionV3) to get a top score in a bottle classification Kaggle challenge. The model predicts how much water or soda a bottle contains.
